80
00:04:31.980 --> 00:04:32.814
Astaga.

81
00:04:33.398 --> 00:04:37.026
Nampaknya dia percaya
anda berkongsi sebahagian daripada kesalahan

82
00:04:37.110 --> 00:04:39.320
